            <paragraph classes="classref-signal" ids="class-scrollcontainer-signal-scroll-ended" names="class_scrollcontainer_signal_scroll_ended"><strong>scroll_ended</strong> <strong>(</strong> <strong>)</strong></paragraph>
            <paragraph>当<emphasis>通过触摸事件</emphasis>拖动可滚动区域而导致滚动停止时发出。当通过拖动滚动条滚动、使用鼠标滚轮滚动、或使用键盘/游戏手柄事件滚动时，<emphasis>不</emphasis>会发出该信号。</paragraph>
            <paragraph><strong>注意：</strong>该信号仅在 Android 或 iOS 上，或在启用 <reference internal="True" refuri="class_projectsettings#class-projectsettings-property-input-devices-pointing-emulate-touch-from-mouse"><inline classes="std std-ref">ProjectSettings.input_devices/pointing/emulate_touch_from_mouse</inline></reference> 时的桌面/Web 平台上发出。</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-scrollcontainer-signal-scroll-started"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-signal" ids="class-scrollcontainer-signal-scroll-started" names="class_scrollcontainer_signal_scroll_started"><strong>scroll_started</strong> <strong>(</strong> <strong>)</strong></paragraph>
