            <paragraph><strong>注意：</strong>该信号仅在 Android 或 iOS 上，或在启用 <reference internal="True" refuri="class_projectsettings#class-projectsettings-property-input-devices-pointing-emulate-touch-from-mouse"><inline classes="std std-ref">ProjectSettings.input_devices/pointing/emulate_touch_from_mouse</inline></reference> 时的桌面/Web 平台上发出。</paragraph>
